metadata.name: Forest of Freedom
metadata.description:
In this magical forest  
Between the trees and leaves  
We found the taste of freedom

In a single tender embrace  
Surrounded by the wilderness  
We were united as one 

--

Gift to the collectors of 'Freedom to Love'. 
Thank you for joining me in this cause and showing that everyone should be free to be who they want to be.  
Also, thank you for your trust and support in me and my work.

--

Models: Florian Hencher & Adam Lee Mroz
